  1→#!/usr/bin/env bun
  2→
  3→/**
  4→ * Ralph Loop - Automated Claude Code Task Executor
  5→ *
  6→ * Based on Geoffrey Huntley's Ralph Wiggum technique:
  7→ * - Fresh context per iteration (new Claude instance each time)
  8→ * - Memory persists through files only (git, progress.txt)
  9→ * - One task per iteration
 10→ * - Completion signal terminates loop
 11→ *
 12→ * Uses Claude CLI's --output-format stream-json for real-time streaming.
 13→ *
 14→ * @see https://ghuntley.com/ralph/
 15→ */
