238→0. Understand Project
239→1. Read ./.claude/progress.txt and identify the most important pending task;
240→   - Specific task prioritization is indicated/tagged/prefixed with '[P'+number+']'
241→   - Tasks tagged with '[P0]' must be done before anything else.
242→   - Tasks tagged with P bigger than 999 (e.g. '[P1000]'), are low-priority
243→   tasks, they should be done when possible, but they must be done
244→   (they are not ignorable); If the task takes longer and there are other
